item.title: PISTOL - Game Over [Neuro Hop, Hip Hop, 100 bpm, WIP]
item.dc:creator: Bassment_Chemists
item.description:
I think the piano level could be a little louder and the synths brought back a little bit.

Love the samples you used.

Yeah mostly I’d say the levels need some work it sounds like there is some clipping at a few points. Which I think is an audio illusion as I don’t think auxy actually lets clipping happen in the way it’s programmed though I could be mistaken.

Also I think you could end it about 30 seconds sooner the last minute and a half gets really repetitive
